text: Jochen Heck (born 27 July 1947) is a German rower who represented West Germany. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics in Mexico City with the men's coxless four where they came sixth. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bremen
